column1: * Please note: This report does not combine crosslisted courses
** Please note: In order to protect student privacy, grade distributions for groups of five or fewer students have been redacted.
*** S/SD and U/UD: In Spring 2020 two new letter grades were created: SD (Satisfactory-Disruption) and UD (Unsatisfactory-Disruption). These new grades are combined with “S” and "U” on this report
